Package com.asemantics.rdfcoder

This package contains the CommandLine access point and the High Level API interface ( RDFCoder ).

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCommandLine
    The Command line RDFCoder utility.
    CoderUtils
    This class contains some general utility methods.

    Filters all java class files inside a dir.
    CoderUtils.JavaJarFilter
    Filters all jar archives inside a dir.
    CoderUtils.JavaSourceFilenameFilter
    Filters all java source files inside a dir.
